---
title: Thai-Inspired Curry Chicken and Mango Burgers with Pickled Jalapeños and Peanut Butter Mayo
description: We've added gently-spiced red curry paste to our chicken patties to give them those Thai vibes! Fresh mango slices add the perfect touch of sweetness to these burgers, while pickled jalapeños cut through the decadent peanut butter mayo condiment. A side of sweet potato wedges completes this burger night!
